CustomField.description: Compare Numeric value of System When to Nurse Recommendation When. Used for reporting.
CustomField.formula: IF( VCC_Nurse_Where_Value__c > VCC_System_Where_Value__c, 'Upgrade', IF(VCC_Nurse_Where_Value__c < VCC_System_Where_Value__c, 'Downgrade', 'No Change'))
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Compare Numeric value of System When to Nurse Recommendation When.
CustomField.label: Where Comparison
